title: Brand New In Lewisville! Poolside Cabanas, Stainless Steel, Granite
posting_body: You will find us conveniently located near Dallas-Fort Worth International Airport, Vista Ridge and Grapevine Mills Mall.
Our community offers spacious one, two and three bedroom floor plans.
Each home is a unique combination of luxury and attention to detail.
Inside our homes you will find a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, soaring nine foot ceilings, contemporary lighting and your own private balcony or patio.
You will enjoy our easy access to public transportation, major freeways and world class shopping.

We offer an executive business center, direct- access garages, gated access, valet trash pick-up, poolside cabanas, a complete fitness center with technogym and top-of-the-line equipment and an icafe with a coffee bar and complimentary wi-fi.
